					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I've always liked the Chaos Insurgency personally&#8230; But this? I like both Langley and Radcliffe, they both opposites to each other completely and almost slip into a cliche with how they are. But they're enjoyable in their own way. Of course, Cactusman is Cactusman. He's great.<br /> But yes, I love how you show the Chaos Insurgency in this tale.</p> 
				 	]]>
