					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Cactusman is amazing, and tales starring Cactusman are amazing by extension.</p> <p>I also enjoy the vibe you throw off in the tale. It is very chaotic and laid-back. Indeed, the antithesis of the Foundation.</p> <p>I do hope there is a sequel (Cactusman 2: The Golden Army).</p> 
				 	]]>
